<L>Arma Virumque cano, Trojae qui primus ab <HI>aris</HI></L>
<L>Italiam, <HI>flatu</HI> profugus <HI>Latinaque</HI> venit</L>
<L>Littora. multum ille et terris <HI>vexatus</HI> et alto,</L>
<L>Vi &s;uper&ucirc;m&mdash;</L>
